    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Bar Mitzvahs and Their Meanings</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Wendy A Marx letter on February 24 article blames parents for turning bar mitzvah parties into spectacles</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>It is the parents who control the purse strings and the ones who instill values. During their time of coming into adulthood we need to remind our children where the emphasis should be without turning this whole, beautiful and memorable event into a three-ring circus.</p>
        <p>WENDY A. MARX  Jericho</p>
      </block>
